Message.SourceString: The aliens could impersonate any one of us… <b>except me.</>

You'll find the Infiltrator soon enough.
I heard they only eat <b>cat food. </>
Hard to hide that habit.

Does it look like I'm blinking with <enemy>vertical eyelids? </>
Ask someone else.

I heard the alien Infiltrator smells just like <enemy>wet leather.</>
And I smell like... <b>me. </>

It's <b>not me...</>
But what if it's <enemy>you? </>

DefaultMessage.SourceString:
It's <b>not me...</>
But what if it's <enemy>you? </>
